{"tid":892423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次開po好想屌臭人之一人一個接受唔到前度/現任嘅on9理由","createTime":"2018-11-07T01:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T10:43:53.000Z","uid":210841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2870d7d45829755c7648b48db8da59011de35df3","tid":892423,"uid":210841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:15:06.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n就我先<br />\n<br />\n條女好鍾意飲酒<br />\n我覺得一個月一兩次怡下情咁<br />\n唔係咩大問題<br />\n屌佢老母<br />\n識得越耐<br />\n飲得越開<br />\n佢老味<br />\n識左唔撚夠一個月開始黎料<br />\n條木嘴當啲酒水唔洗錢💰咁<br />\n起勢咁灌落個胃度<br />\n個下好似望住啲通渠佬通渠咁<br />\n唉都算啦<br />\n條女自己揀嘅<br />\n點撚知佢後尾醉到成個人小兒麻痺咁款<br />\n差在未係bar度上演葉問一個打十個（成日meet，咬，打我夠三角肌，當正沙包咁）<br />\n<br />\n廢話唔多講<br />\n入正題<br />\n佢比我chok到料<br />\n之前同好fd嘅男性友人飲到醉曬<br />\n跟住搞埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到呢度覺得自己識佢之前已經比人綠緊咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ba28061d6084b3ba544c742e1e0433d4872ae8","tid":892423,"uid":214997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:19:55.000Z","msg":"唔係之前 係一直都綠緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919f7de9f9eda292a8d6e17e44e9a219c23d58c6","tid":892423,"uid":210841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45ba28061d6084b3ba544c742e1e0433d4872ae8","tid":892423,"uid":214997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:19:55.000Z","msg":"唔係之前 係一直都綠緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"係一齊之前嘅事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/